### 🎨 Design Features

- **Glass-morphism UI:** Modern frosted glass effect with backdrop blur
- **Gradient Backgrounds:** Purple gradient theme (#667eea → #764ba2)
- **Smooth Animations:** CSS transitions with AOS library integration
- **Intersection Observer:** Performance-optimized scroll animations
- **Responsive Grid:** Mobile-first Bootstrap grid system
- **Custom Components:** Reusable Blade components for consistency

