## 📋 Requirements

Before you begin, ensure you have the following installed on your system:

| Requirement | Version | Purpose |
|-------------|---------|---------|
| **PHP** | >= 8.1 | Backend runtime |
| **Composer** | Latest | PHP dependency management |
| **MySQL** | >= 5.7 or MariaDB >= 10.3 | Database server |
| **Node.js** | >= 14.x | Asset compilation |
| **NPM** | >= 6.x | JavaScript package management |

**Recommended Development Environment:**
- XAMPP / LAMPP / WAMP (includes PHP & MySQL)
- Git for version control
- VS Code or PHPStorm as IDE

