## 🎯 Usage

### 🌐 Accessing the Application

| Section | URL | Purpose |
|---------|-----|---------|
| **Homepage** | `http://localhost:8000` | Public-facing website |
| **Admin Login** | `http://localhost:8000/admin/login` | Admin panel authentication |
| **Admin Dashboard** | `http://localhost:8000/admin/dashboard` | CMS dashboard (after login) |

### 🔐 Default Admin Credentials

```
Email: mamaruf317@gmail.com
Password: admin123
```

> ⚠️ **Security Note:** Change these credentials immediately after first login in production!

### 📝 Creating Additional Admins

Run the admin creation script:

```bash
php create_admin.php
```

Or use Laravel Tinker:

```bash
php artisan tinker
>>> User::create(['name' => 'Admin Name', 'email' => 'admin@example.com', 'password' => bcrypt('password')]);
```

